featured_reviews.review_id: Nice masjid/mosque, it's clean nice and effort is being put in. When I was younger I used to come here often and attend the barbecues and children events they had. Really liked it and it's a nice staple of the community. They also have events now which are really cool for the youth.

featured_reviews.review_id: Masjid Annur Islamic Center is one of the masjids I visited in Sacramento. I came here back in May of 2022 with my cousins and family members. Very peaceful and welcoming community bringing all Muslims of all communities, especially coming from an area close to San Francisco. This place will always allow you to reset in your Salah and walk out in peace, SubhanAllah. Such a place will promote nothing but happiness and satisfaction. Will come again soon, InshaAllah.
